{"name":"Quick Shield Block","type":"feat","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/features/feats/feats.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>You can bring your shield into place with hardly a thought. At the start of each of your turns, you gain an additional reaction that you can use only to @Compendium[pf2e.feats-srd.jM72TjJ965jocBV8]{Shield Block}.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Pathfinder Core Rulebook, Stalwart Defender"},"traits":{"value":["archetype"],"rarity":"common","custom":""},"rules":[],"slug":"quick-shield-block","schema":{"version":0.75,"lastMigration":null},"level":{"value":8},"featType":{"value":"ancestry"},"onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"passive"},"actionCategory":{"value":""},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[{"value":"shield block"},{"value":"Stalwart Defender Dedication"}]},"location":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"gKRAixZcnc2H4VRx":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.pf2e.feats-srd.pRqcm5P2ZFihSpVI"}},"_id":"1IXz6TM1i5uXyBIu"}
{"_id":"3FxmQOEnS5Ep5DHd","name":"Unyielding Defender","type":"feat","img":"icons/magic/control/buff-strength-muscle-damage-orange.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><strong>Frequency</strong>: Once per 10 minutes</p>\n<hr />\n<p>Your dedication to hold against all odds is such that only death can remove you from your charge. When you reach 0 hit points and would fall @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.fBnFDH2MTzgFijKf]{Unconscious}, you instead remain standing in @Compendium[pf2e-stalwart-defender.stalwart-defender-actions.CvudRhesukRV1TDI]{Stalwart Stance}. You are otherwise still considered unconscious with 0 hit points and potentially @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.yZRUzMqrMmfLu0V1]{Dying} as normal but effects tied to your stance remain active and if you regain consciousness you remain in your stance.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Stalwart Defender"},"traits":{"value":["archetype"],"rarity":"common","custom":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.75,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2022-06-02T11:03:13.423-05:00","version":{"schema":null,"foundry":"9.269","system":"3.10.3.11650"}}},"level":{"value":18},"featType":{"value":"archetype"},"onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"passive"},"actionCategory":{"value":""},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[{"value":"Stalwart Defender Dedication"}]},"location":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"gKRAixZcnc2H4VRx":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"86IaZXn5VjVNpG2Z","name":"Defender's Courage","type":"feat","img":"icons/skills/social/intimidation-impressing.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>You refuse to flee the place you&rsquo;ve chosen to defend. Whenever you become @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.TBSHQspnbcqxsmjL]{Frightened}, reduce the condition value by 1 (to a minimum of 0). If an effect would cause you to be @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.sDPxOjQ9kx2RZE8D]{Fleeing}, you can choose to become @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.6uEgoh53GbXuHpTF]{Paralyzed} until the start of your next turn instead.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>"},"source":{"value":"Stalwart Defender"},"traits":{"value":["archetype"],"rarity":"common","custom":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.75,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2022-06-02T11:03:13.423-05:00","version":{"schema":null,"foundry":"9.269","system":"3.10.3.11650"}}},"level":{"value":8},"featType":{"value":"archetype"},"onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"passive"},"actionCategory":{"value":""},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[{"value":"Stalwart Defender Dedication"}]},"location":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"gKRAixZcnc2H4VRx":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"DNar60fwdnvpyP9h","name":"Don't Cross the Line","type":"feat","img":"icons/environment/settlement/fence-wooden-picket.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><strong>Requirements</strong> You are @Compendium[pf2e-stalwart-defender.stalwart-defender-actions.CvudRhesukRV1TDI]{Stalwart Stance}</p>\n<hr />\n<p>You carve a line in the ground that none shall pass so long as you guard it. Pick three contiguous, unoccupied squares adjacent to you that form a straight line. These squares are considered occupied by you for the purposes of other creatures' movement. The effects of this ability immediately end if you leave Stalwart Stance.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>"},"source":{"value":"Stalwart Defender"},"traits":{"value":["archetype"],"rarity":"common","custom":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.75,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2022-06-02T11:03:13.423-05:00","version":{"schema":null,"foundry":"9.269","system":"3.10.3.11650"}}},"level":{"value":10},"featType":{"value":"archetype"},"onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"action"},"actionCategory":{"value":"defensive"},"actions":{"value":2},"prerequisites":{"value":[{"value":"Stalwart Defender Dedication"}]},"location":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"gKRAixZcnc2H4VRx":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"J2YGbYf2unZwBubv","name":"Stalwart's Safe Zone","type":"feat","img":"icons/magic/defensive/barrier-shield-dome-deflect-teal.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><strong>Trigger</strong>&nbsp;An ally is targeted by a spell attack, cone, or line and your position could provide lesser cover, cover, or greater cover to that ally from the source</p>\n<hr />\n<p>You continuously maneuver yourself in the way of attacks that would harm your allies. You attempt to counteract that effect. Your counteract level for this attempt is equal to half your level rounded up, and you use your Fortitude save as your counteract modifier. If you successfully counteract the effect, instead of ending, the effect targets you, but not any allies you provide lesser cover, cover, or greater cover to.</p>\n<p><strong>Special</strong> if you also have @Compendium[pf2e-stalwart-defender.stalwart-defender-feats.lrI7l9AeO3kJ5RKT]{Get Behind Me!}, You also prevent allies within your reach from being targeted when you succeed, even if you do not grant them any form of cover.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>"},"source":{"value":"Stalwart Defender"},"traits":{"value":["archetype"],"rarity":"common","custom":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.75,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2022-06-02T11:03:13.423-05:00","version":{"schema":null,"foundry":"9.269","system":"3.10.3.11650"}}},"level":{"value":18},"featType":{"value":"archetype"},"onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"reaction"},"actionCategory":{"value":"defensive"},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[{"value":"Stalwart Defender Dedication"},{"value":"Mirrored Fortress"}]},"location":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"gKRAixZcnc2H4VRx":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"MNIH0ekuDncThll9","name":"Shield Warden (Stalwart Defender)","type":"feat","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/features/feats/feats.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>You use your shield to protect your allies as well as yourself. When you have a shield raised, you can use your Shield Block reaction when an attack is made against an ally adjacent to you. If you do, the shield prevents that ally from taking damage instead of preventing you from taking damage, following the normal rules for Shield Block.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Pathfinder Core Rulebook, Stalwart Defender"},"traits":{"value":["archetype"],"rarity":"common","custom":""},"rules":[],"slug":"shield-warden-fighter","schema":{"version":0.75,"lastMigration":null},"level":{"value":8},"featType":{"value":"archetype"},"onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"passive"},"actionCategory":{"value":""},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[{"value":"shield block"},{"value":"Stalwart Defender Dedication"}]},"location":""},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"gKRAixZcnc2H4VRx":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.pf2e.feats-srd.5vXc2s2siR1ihpBT"}}}
{"_id":"MonjizUmnWeQxSEv","name":"Stalwart Halt","type":"feat","img":"icons/skills/melee/strike-chain-whip-blue.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><strong>Trigger </strong>A creature within your reach uses a move action or leaves a square during a move action it&rsquo;s using.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>You strike out when your foe tries to flee. Make a melee Strike against the triggering creature. If the attack is a hit and the trigger was a move action, your Strike deals no damage, but it disrupts that action.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Stalwart Defender"},"traits":{"value":["archetype"],"rarity":"common","custom":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.75,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2022-06-02T11:03:13.423-05:00","version":{"schema":null,"foundry":"9.269","system":"3.10.3.11650"}}},"level":{"value":8},"featType":{"value":"archetype"},"onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"reaction"},"actionCategory":{"value":"defensive"},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[{"value":"Stalwart Defender Dedication"}]},"location":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"gKRAixZcnc2H4VRx":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"OYkQVezNJBJP0kS9","name":"Defender of the Sky","type":"feat","img":"icons/magic/air/air-smoke-casting.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><strong>Requirements </strong>You are in @Compendium[pf2e-stalwart-defender.stalwart-defender-actions.CvudRhesukRV1TDI]{Stalwart Stance}</p>\n<hr />\n<p>Even the air yields to your claim to plant yourself in a sturdy stance. You Stride up to half your speed and you may treat the air as solid ground. You can ascend and descend in this way at a maximum of a 45-degree angle. This movement does not end Stalwart Stance, but you immediately fall when your Stalwart Stance ends.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>"},"source":{"value":"Stalwart Defender"},"traits":{"value":["air","archetype","flourish","magical","transmutation"],"rarity":"common","custom":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.75,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2022-06-02T11:03:13.423-05:00","version":{"schema":null,"foundry":"9.269","system":"3.10.3.11650"}}},"level":{"value":16},"featType":{"value":"archetype"},"onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"action"},"actionCategory":{"value":"interaction"},"actions":{"value":1},"prerequisites":{"value":[{"value":"Stalwart Defender Dedication"}]},"location":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"gKRAixZcnc2H4VRx":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"Q9v71UBCTUkblzlc","name":"Mobile Bulwark","type":"feat","img":"icons/equipment/shoulder/pauldron-ridged-copper-green.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>You are so accustomed to planting your feet that to do so doesn&rsquo;t even cross your mind. You become permanently @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.nlCjDvLMf2EkV2dl]{Quickened}. You can use your extra action only to enter @Compendium[pf2e-stalwart-defender.stalwart-defender-actions.CvudRhesukRV1TDI]{Stalwart Stance}, Raise a Shield, or Step.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Stalwart Defender"},"traits":{"value":["archetype"],"rarity":"common","custom":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.75,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2022-06-02T11:03:13.423-05:00","version":{"schema":null,"foundry":"9.269","system":"3.10.3.11650"}}},"level":{"value":20},"featType":{"value":"archetype"},"onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"passive"},"actionCategory":{"value":""},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[{"value":"Stalwart Defender Dedication"}]},"location":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"gKRAixZcnc2H4VRx":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"R1W3MMrQXTnH71k0","name":"Stalwart Defender Dedication","type":"feat","img":"icons/equipment/head/helm-barbute-engraved-steel.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>You are a stalwart defender and you hold the line against any foe. Be it dragon, demon, or undead, nothing will make you shirk from your duty to protect those around you. You gain a +2 circumstance bonus to your Fortitude or Reflex saves and DCs against any Forced Movement effects. In addition, if any effect would force you to move, you can reduce the distance you would move by 10ft. If this reduces the distance to 0ft, you don&rsquo;t move. You also gain @Compendium[pf2e-stalwart-defender.stalwart-defender-actions.CvudRhesukRV1TDI]{Stalwart Stance}.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>"},"source":{"value":"Stalwart Defender"},"traits":{"value":["archetype","dedication"],"rarity":"common","custom":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.75,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2022-06-02T11:03:13.423-05:00","version":{"schema":null,"foundry":"9.269","system":"3.10.3.11650"}}},"level":{"value":6},"featType":{"value":"archetype"},"onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"passive"},"actionCategory":{"value":""},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[]},"location":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"gKRAixZcnc2H4VRx":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"SHXPoW1wX6FYUZYI","name":"Stalwart's Quake","type":"feat","img":"icons/magic/earth/barrier-stone-explosion-debris.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>Your stance is so grounded to the earth, that you can cause it crack and break around you. Creatures on the ground within your reach take damage equal to your Strength modifier (minimum 0), which they can resist with a @Check[type:fortitude|basic:true] save against your Class DC or spellcasting DC, whichever is higher. In addition, all spaces adjacent to you become difficult terrain.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Stalwart Defender"},"traits":{"value":["archetype","earth","magical","transmutation"],"rarity":"common","custom":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.75,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2022-06-02T11:03:13.423-05:00","version":{"schema":null,"foundry":"9.269","system":"3.10.3.11650"}}},"level":{"value":10},"featType":{"value":"archetype"},"onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"action"},"actionCategory":{"value":"offensive"},"actions":{"value":1},"prerequisites":{"value":[{"value":"Stalwart Defender Dedication"}]},"location":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"gKRAixZcnc2H4VRx":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"TITJFU5RZ4Hw3Gjh","name":"Defender of the Earth","type":"feat","img":"icons/magic/defensive/armor-stone-skin.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><strong>Requirements</strong> You are in @Compendium[pf2e-stalwart-defender.stalwart-defender-actions.CvudRhesukRV1TDI]{Stalwart Stance}</p>\n<hr />\n<p>Even the ground below you becomes difficult to pass through and you can sense when creatures have the audacity to try. You gain a new sense: imprecise tremorsense with a range of 20 feet so long as you remain in Stalwart Stance. Every square below you within range of your tremorsense counts as being within your reach for the purposes of Stalwart Stance as you shake the earth beneath your feet.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>"},"source":{"value":"Stalwart Defender"},"traits":{"value":["archetype","earth","magical","transmutation"],"rarity":"common","custom":""},"rules":[{"acuity":"imprecise","key":"Sense","label":"PF2E.SensesTremorsense","range":20,"selector":"tremorsense","predicate":{"all":["self:effect:stalwart-stance"]}}],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.75,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2022-06-02T11:03:13.423-05:00","version":{"schema":null,"foundry":"9.269","system":"3.10.3.11650"}}},"level":{"value":16},"featType":{"value":"archetype"},"onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"action"},"actionCategory":{"value":"interaction"},"actions":{"value":1},"prerequisites":{"value":[{"value":"Stalwart Defender Dedication"}]},"location":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"gKRAixZcnc2H4VRx":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.TITJFU5RZ4Hw3Gjh"}}}
{"_id":"Ug90vMNqiPTPol5k","name":"Reach Over Me!","type":"feat","img":"icons/skills/melee/hand-grip-staff-blue.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>You can huddle down in your defensive stance allowing your allies to reach over you. Until the start of your next turn, your allies may choose to add the Reach trait to their melee strikes, but only if their attack would pass through your square. You still provide @Compendium[pf2e.equipment-effects.I9lfZUiCwMiGogVi]{Lesser Cover or Cover} for these attacks as normal.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Stalwart Defender"},"traits":{"value":["archetype"],"rarity":"common","custom":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.75,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2022-06-02T11:03:13.423-05:00","version":{"schema":null,"foundry":"9.269","system":"3.10.3.11650"}}},"level":{"value":10},"featType":{"value":"archetype"},"onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"action"},"actionCategory":{"value":"offensive"},"actions":{"value":1},"prerequisites":{"value":[{"value":"Stalwart Defender Dedication"}]},"location":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"gKRAixZcnc2H4VRx":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"YLbMPG2tzkDQtHuO","name":"Even in Death","type":"feat","img":"icons/magic/unholy/strike-body-explode-disintegrate.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>You have sworn an oath to protect the spot you defend, even after you die. Choose one creature to be your Oath Holder when you activate this feat. When you would die while in @Compendium[pf2e-stalwart-defender.stalwart-defender-actions.CvudRhesukRV1TDI]{Stalwart Stance}, you instead remain standing in Stalwart Stance until your Oath Holder, or someone they designate, releases you from your charge or your body is completely destroyed. You are still considered dead while in this state and can take no actions.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Stalwart Defender"},"traits":{"value":["archetype"],"rarity":"common","custom":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.75,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2022-06-02T11:03:13.423-05:00","version":{"schema":null,"foundry":"9.269","system":"3.10.3.11650"}}},"level":{"value":20},"featType":{"value":"archetype"},"onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"passive"},"actionCategory":{"value":""},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[{"value":"Stalwart Defender Dedication"},{"value":"Unyielding Defender"}]},"location":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"gKRAixZcnc2H4VRx":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"aoSw1huWbNdxVGz3","name":"Defender's Recovery","type":"feat","img":"icons/magic/life/heart-cross-strong-green.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><strong>Requirements</strong>&nbsp;You are in Stalwart Stance</p>\n<hr />\n<p>You take a deep, restorative breath. You gain temporary Hit Points equal to half your level plus the number of rounds you have been in Stalwart Stance. The maximum number of temporary Hit Points you can gain from this ability is equal to two times your level.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Stalwart Defender"},"traits":{"value":["archetype","concentrate"],"rarity":"common","custom":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.75,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2022-06-02T11:03:13.423-05:00","version":{"schema":null,"foundry":"9.269","system":"3.10.3.11650"}}},"level":{"value":8},"featType":{"value":"archetype"},"onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"action"},"actionCategory":{"value":"defensive"},"actions":{"value":1},"prerequisites":{"value":[{"value":"Stalwart Defender Dedication"}]},"location":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"gKRAixZcnc2H4VRx":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"caJbLfABreDQxGqX","name":"One Man Legion","type":"feat","img":"icons/environment/people/infantry-army.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>Your carved line becomes alive with purpose all its own, allowing your force of will to apply across an unlimited area. When you use @Compendium[pf2e-stalwart-defender.stalwart-defender-feats.DNar60fwdnvpyP9h]{Don't Cross the Line}, you may pick any number of contiguous, unoccupied squares that form a straight line so long as your current space is a part of that line. If you choose spaces that are beyond your reach, phantom echoes of yourself appear at regular intervals along the line.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>"},"source":{"value":"Stalwart Defender"},"traits":{"value":["archetype","conjuration","magical"],"rarity":"common","custom":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.75,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2022-06-02T11:03:13.423-05:00","version":{"schema":null,"foundry":"9.269","system":"3.10.3.11650"}}},"level":{"value":20},"featType":{"value":"archetype"},"onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"passive"},"actionCategory":{"value":""},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[{"value":"Stalwart Defender Dedication"},{"value":"Don't Cross the Line"}]},"location":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"gKRAixZcnc2H4VRx":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"dnZsrXzOjQMxbeGa","name":"Defender's Reflexes","type":"feat","img":"icons/magic/time/hourglass-tilted-glowing-gold.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>Stopping creatures from moving is second nature to you. At the start of each of your turns, you gain an additional reaction that you can use only for Stalwart Defender reactions.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Stalwart Defender"},"traits":{"value":["archetype"],"rarity":"common","custom":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.75,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2022-06-02T11:03:13.423-05:00","version":{"schema":null,"foundry":"9.269","system":"3.10.3.11650"}}},"level":{"value":16},"featType":{"value":"archetype"},"onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"passive"},"actionCategory":{"value":""},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[{"value":"Stalwart Defender Dedication"}]},"location":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"gKRAixZcnc2H4VRx":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"i4L4fF4cD9hEtEc9","name":"Defender's Rush","type":"feat","img":"icons/skills/movement/feet-winged-boots-glowing-yellow.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><strong>Trigger</strong> an ally within range of your movement speed is hit or critically hit by a Strike or spell attack</p>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong> You are in @Compendium[pf2e-stalwart-defender.stalwart-defender-actions.CvudRhesukRV1TDI]{Stalwart Stance}</p>\n<hr />\n<p>You rush to the side of an ally to intercept the blow for them. Stride towards the triggering ally (or Burrow, Climb, Fly, or Swim if you have an associated speed and its use is appropriate) and then resolve the attack as if it succeeded against your AC. If the attack was a critical success, it only counts as a critical success against you if it would normally against your AC. After resolving the attack, your Stalwart Stance ends.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>"},"source":{"value":"Stalwart Defender"},"traits":{"value":["archetype"],"rarity":"common","custom":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.75,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2022-06-02T11:03:13.423-05:00","version":{"schema":null,"foundry":"9.269","system":"3.10.3.11650"}}},"level":{"value":14},"featType":{"value":"archetype"},"onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"passive"},"actionCategory":{"value":""},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[{"value":"Stalwart Defender Dedication"}]},"location":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"gKRAixZcnc2H4VRx":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"kuusUx8iQeYIoFnp","name":"Toss Me!","type":"feat","img":"icons/skills/movement/arrow-upward-yellow.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>You can ready yourself for an ally to throw you while remaining grounded in your stance. Once, before the start of your next turn, an ally can attempt to throw you towards your enemies. Your ally must succeed at an @Check[type:athletics] Athletics check against your Fortitude DC with a +2 circumstance bonus. If they do, you are thrown a number of feet equal to half your movement speed rounded down. This movement doesn&rsquo;t end your @Compendium[pf2e-stalwart-defender.stalwart-defender-actions.CvudRhesukRV1TDI]{Stalwart Stance}.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Stalwart Defender"},"traits":{"value":["archetype"],"rarity":"common","custom":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.75,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2022-06-02T11:03:13.423-05:00","version":{"schema":null,"foundry":"9.269","system":"3.10.3.11650"}}},"level":{"value":12},"featType":{"value":"archetype"},"onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"action"},"actionCategory":{"value":"offensive"},"actions":{"value":1},"prerequisites":{"value":[{"value":"Stalwart Defender Dedication"}]},"location":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"gKRAixZcnc2H4VRx":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"lWzeOnWFTkpFqE1m","name":"Boundless Defense","type":"feat","img":"icons/magic/time/hourglass-brown-orange.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>Your reaction speed to defend those around you is the stuff of legends. At the start of each enemy&rsquo;s turn, you gain a reaction you can use only during that turn to use reactions that could be granted by the stalwart defender archetype or Shield Block.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Stalwart Defender"},"traits":{"value":["archetype"],"rarity":"common","custom":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.75,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2022-06-02T11:03:13.423-05:00","version":{"schema":null,"foundry":"9.269","system":"3.10.3.11650"}}},"level":{"value":20},"featType":{"value":"archetype"},"onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"free"},"actionCategory":{"value":""},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[{"value":"Stalwart Defender Dedication"},{"value":"Defender's Reflexes"}]},"location":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"gKRAixZcnc2H4VRx":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"lqQDYGzx1azfCbTM","name":"Unsurprised Defender","type":"feat","img":"icons/skills/melee/maneuver-daggers-paired-orange.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>You guard yourself and others from every angle. You aren&rsquo;t @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.AJh5ex99aV6VTggg]{Flat-Footed} to @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.iU0fEDdBp3rXpTMC]{Hidden}, @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.VRSef5y1LmL2Hkjf]{Undetected}, or flanking creatures of your level or lower, or creatures of your level or lower using @Compendium[pf2e.classfeatures.w6rMqmGzhUahdnA7]{Surprise Attack}. However, they can still help their allies flank.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Stalwart Defender"},"traits":{"value":["archetype"],"rarity":"common","custom":""},"rules":[{"key":"ActiveEffectLike","mode":"override","path":"data.attributes.flanking.flatFootable","value":"@actor.level"}],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.75,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2022-06-02T11:03:13.423-05:00","version":{"schema":null,"foundry":"9.269","system":"3.10.3.11650"}}},"level":{"value":12},"featType":{"value":"archetype"},"onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"passive"},"actionCategory":{"value":""},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[{"value":"Stalwart Defender Dedication"}]},"location":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"gKRAixZcnc2H4VRx":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"lrI7l9AeO3kJ5RKT","name":"Get Behind Me!","type":"feat","img":"icons/magic/control/silhouette-hold-change-blue.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><strong>Trigger</strong>&nbsp;You and at least one ally within your reach would make a reflex save against an effect that would deal hit point damage</p>\n<hr />\n<p>You take the brunt of an attack to shield your allies from harm. You grant @Compendium[pf2e.equipment-effects.I9lfZUiCwMiGogVi]{Greater Cover} to all allies within your reach for their Reflex save, but you treat the result of your saving throw as one degree worse after you roll.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>"},"source":{"value":"Stalwart Defender"},"traits":{"value":["archetype"],"rarity":"common","custom":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.75,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2022-06-02T11:03:13.423-05:00","version":{"schema":null,"foundry":"9.269","system":"3.10.3.11650"}}},"level":{"value":14},"featType":{"value":"archetype"},"onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"reaction"},"actionCategory":{"value":"defensive"},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[{"value":"Stalwart Defender Dedication"}]},"location":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"gKRAixZcnc2H4VRx":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"qXbd9cCajTGn8yUx","name":"Mirrored Fortress","type":"feat","img":"icons/magic/defensive/shield-barrier-deflect-gold.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><strong>Trigger </strong>An opponent casting a spell that targets you fails a spell attack roll against your AC.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>You take the spell head-on in order to reflect it back against the triggering opponent. Treat the failed spell attack roll as if it succeeded against your AC, then make a ranged attack against the triggering creature using your highest proficiency with a ranged weapon. If you can cast spells, you can make a spell attack roll instead. If you succeed, your opponent takes the effects of a successful spell attack roll for their own spell (or the effects of a critical success if your attack roll was a critical success).</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>"},"source":{"value":"Stalwart Defender"},"traits":{"value":["archetype"],"rarity":"common","custom":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.75,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2022-06-02T11:03:13.423-05:00","version":{"schema":null,"foundry":"9.269","system":"3.10.3.11650"}}},"level":{"value":12},"featType":{"value":"archetype"},"onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"reaction"},"actionCategory":{"value":"defensive"},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[{"value":"Stalwart Defender Dedication"}]},"location":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"gKRAixZcnc2H4VRx":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"w7Nfc9atYuorFMRN","name":"Defender's Strike","type":"feat","img":"icons/skills/melee/swords-triple-orange.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>You slowly reposition while delivering a distracting strike. Either Step and then Strike, or Strike and then Step. This Step does not end @Compendium[pf2e-stalwart-defender.stalwart-defender-actions.CvudRhesukRV1TDI]{Stalwart Stance} and may be used even in difficult terrain.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Stalwart Defender"},"traits":{"value":["archetype","flourish"],"rarity":"common","custom":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.75,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2022-06-02T11:03:13.423-05:00","version":{"schema":null,"foundry":"9.269","system":"3.10.3.11650"}}},"level":{"value":8},"featType":{"value":"archetype"},"onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"action"},"actionCategory":{"value":"offensive"},"actions":{"value":1},"prerequisites":{"value":[{"value":"Stalwart Defender Dedication"}]},"location":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"gKRAixZcnc2H4VRx":3},"flags":{}}
